Invocation Name: my nest
des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. Do you have a friendly bear with a thick rich coat, and a nest of fledglings in them, then listen to this story of a fledgling you name who does not grow feathers and wings strong enough to fly away, in the story, you take the help of the timeless medicine woman in you to dress him up in matching feathers, till he is strong enough to fly away, the 'graduation' in old medicine woman's flight academy? Will the fledglings graduate to flight, or will they remain hungry for food. Listen to this story as old medicine woman, teaches the fledglings the prayer to the wind, as they graduate to flight and leave Bhaloo bears coat.
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
